  "duration": 75.9800033569336,
  "fullText": "Good morning Today is the last day of our agentic coding training squad 2 20 participants are graduating and I just thought of three tips for sustained performance and learning in the agentic era First tip is that join the community be active in discord server or groups or meetups and so on Second tip is share your screen If you share your screen you get so much feedback and from other people they are very open to helping you And third because working with agents can be really overwhelming you should take a walk after an exhaustive session That really helps me to clarify my thinking and gather the thoughts Hope this helps"
